    <Paragraph FontSize="22">Required UI Automation Tree Structure
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>The following table depicts the <Run>Control View</Run>
 and the <Run>Content View</Run>
 of the UI Automation tree that pertains to calendar controls and describes what can be contained in each view. For more information on the UI Automation tree, see <Hyperlink NavigateUri="03b98058-bdb3-47a0-8ff7-45e6cdf67166.xaml">UI Automation Tree Overview</Hyperlink>
. 
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph><Run FontWeight="Bold"/>
    </Paragraph>

